Er, no, not groups as such, I don't think, no, er, but that, it was in connection with the, er, church or the chapel, er, there wasn't anything like that, er, in politics, for 
instance, no, sometimes the M.P. would come down and, er, perhaps, er, have a meeting occasionally, but not many groups of people like there are today.
