spectable or better or this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 What, our friends? Oh, we ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 .. or among the people in your area.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Well, we'd be, we'd be one of the, well, I should think we'd be about average, because my, my father was a, a good tradesman and h
e had, he was a skilled carpenter, and he got good wages when he was working, so we'd be amongst I suppose, er, the better, above the labouring class, when, when we'd got, when father was working although we had a large family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 In your area who was thought to be the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 In our area? Oh, usually the tradesmen, or the shops, you know, or the publican, ye-.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 What about the people like the schoolteacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Oh, yes ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 And minister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Oh, yes, yes, they were, oh, yes, they were regarded as er, as principal people, yes, schoolteachers, and, er, the minister.
