\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 There wasn't anybody else you called Sir?
