\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Oh, yes, we'd call, oh, yes, yes, we used to call Sir to, er, nearly all the tradesmen and, er, people who were better off than ourselves
