\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 I wondered if certain sort of people went to chapel and certain sorts of people went to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Yes, but I didn't, I, I didn't notice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 You don't think it made ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Any difference, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Would you say it was possible at that time to move from one ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 One, er ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11798551 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 Class of people to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198963 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12807994\charrsid15749485 From one class of people to another? Er, oh, yes, I think, er, you could improve, improve your status, you mean,
 yes, oh, yes, if you, er, such as my grandmother went into, into business, you see, well that improved her status. She, she was looked upon, er, better than before she did go into business.
